name: "XII" CD Pressing
description:
Limited edition, die-cut CD version of our sophomore album, XII, is now available!

Package includes artwork + booklet containing lyrics, credits and photos, plus sweet CD quality master mixes of:

1. Ritual Dancer
2. Moonlight Desires
3. Time Will Crawl
4. Days of Summer
5. The Hands That Rule The World
6. Dover
7. Love & Devotion
8. Fury On Earth
9. Electrimotion
10. Things Fall Apart
11. Human Nature
12. XII

name: XII Double-Sided Poster
description:
19"x 10" XII Artwork Poster printed double-sided on hi-gloss heavy stock.

Side 1: Metallic XII cover design
Side 2: Celestial secret cover photo

Photography by Maxime Bocken, Design by The White Room
